Nodes.Name: Replace
Nodes.LongDescription:
Strip Parent tags. 
Compiling multiple full payloads appends closing parent tags. 
This replace removes these tags giving us a properly structured payload

Name: Ramp Compile List of Vendors
Description: This Workflow retrieves a paginated list of vendors from Ramp, processes and aggregates the results, and outputs a consolidated vendor list. It handles pagination, data mapping, and formatting to ensure a clean, structured output.
